publisher			Jeff Trier							
publish_time	 2015年4月20日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Shadow Hunter is a casual deductive puzzle game with RPG elements.  As a Shadow Hunter, you must use your senses to detect dangers and artifacts beneath the endless darkness that spreads throughout the land.  Anti-light, the dimension and dimensional darkness from beyond the void gate, threatens to swallow us all. You must quest to find the Shadow Gate Fragments, to destroy the Anti-light menace.16 areas to explore.Deductive mini-games.Random events.Local high-score list.Great horror atmosphere.Turn-based.						
title	 Shadow Hunter			
